# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:14
translate chinese rebap5_ddd1770f:

    # rb "Oh, she's not very happy about it."
    rb "哦，她对此不太高兴。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:15
translate chinese rebap5_2a6b2bcb:

    # rb "She's doing the whole pity party thing. Trying to make me feel bad for leaving her {i}all alone{/i}."
    rb "她正搞那一套自怜自艾的把戏，试图让我因为把她{i}独自一人{/i}留下而感到内疚。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:17
translate chinese rebap5_f4434fb9:

    # rb "I'm like, dang Mama! I'm just moving across town."
    rb "我心想，天哪，老妈！我只是搬到城另一头而已。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:19
translate chinese rebap5_dc9f7362:

    # rb "It ain't like I'm moving to Mars! Or California, or something."
    rb "又不是搬去火星！或者加州什么的。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:21
translate chinese rebap5_e8401a70:

    # rb "But she has been doing a little more on her own, now that Mickey and I ain't doing everything for her."
    rb "不过自从米奇和我不再事事包办后，她确实开始多做些自己的事了。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:22
translate chinese rebap5_7e5ae73b:

    # rb "She's been cooking for herself and doing her own laundry some."
    rb "她会自己做饭，偶尔也洗洗衣服。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:23
translate chinese rebap5_e5bea429:

    # rb "I'm hopin' that this will help pull her out of this funk she's been in since Daddy died."
    rb "我希望这能帮她走出爸爸去世后一直陷在的低谷。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:24
translate chinese rebap5_43991a04:

    # pc "I hope so too."
    pc "我也希望如此。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:26
translate chinese rebap5_ea97738a:

    # rb "Mama's a good person."
    rb "妈妈是个好人。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:27
translate chinese rebap5_765219f9:

    # rb "She frustrates the heck out of me sometimes, but I still love her and want her to be happy."
    rb "虽然她有时真把我气得够呛，但我依然爱她，希望她能开心。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:28
translate chinese rebap5_730f1fcf:

    # rb "She's been in a bad place for a while, but she used to be a really good Mama."
    rb "她这阵子过得挺糟糕，但以前她可是个非常称职的妈妈。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:30
translate chinese rebap5_4f864ba4:

    # rb "I'm lucky that I had two good parents. I know a lot of people who don't have that."
    rb "我有幸拥有两位好父母。我知道很多人可没这般幸运。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:31
translate chinese rebap5_0b5ae046:

    # pc "Well they did a good job with you, that's for sure."
    pc "嗯，他们把你带得挺好，这点毋庸置疑。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:33
translate chinese rebap5_54953312:

    # rb "A fifty percent success rate, I guess, because Mickey turned out to be a real farthead."
    rb "大概成功率五成吧，毕竟米奇最后成了个十足的混蛋。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:34
translate chinese rebap5_4533d803:

    # rb "I don't think you can blame it on them though."
    rb "不过我觉得不能怪他们。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:35
translate chinese rebap5_af217060:

    # pc "Some people are just born bad."
    pc "有些人天生就是坏的。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap5.rpy:3
    old "To have this conversation, you must first have had the conversation about when she is moving out."
    new "能聊到这个话题，说明你们之前肯定已经讨论过她什么时候搬出去的事了。"

